DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this Clinical study was to evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of bongros-BMP compared to Bio-oss for Regeneration of alveolar bone tissue after Maxillary sinus floor augmentation.
DOC.brief_title: Efficacy and Safety of Bongros-BMP Compared to Bio-oss for Regeneration of Alveolar Bone Tissue After Maxillary Sinus Floor Augmentation
